## Prompt 4: Git [.gitignore](file:///Users/vikasahlawat/Documents/Showrunner/.gitignore) Strategy & Git Panel UI

```
You are working on the Showrunner project at /Users/vikasahlawat/Documents/Showrunner.

TASK: Fix the .gitignore strategy for story projects and build a Git Panel UI component.

